snippet.textDisplay:
If you want to experience the true masterpiece, just listen to their father — Tufail Niazi.
Most people say that the real pain in their voice hits when the lyrical part about the angel arrives.
They tried to recreate their father's magic, but couldn’t fully capture the soul he brought to the song.
Don’t take my word for it — listen to "Main Ni Jana Kheriyan De Naal" by Tufail Niazi yourself.
